        "body" : "Probably until we deprecate v1 (if there's ever a v2).\r\nGiven that removing the alpha API (which is actually the beta API), would break all the plugins that were written since 1.13, and require:\r\n- For vendors, a code change (revendoring) and a new image\r\n- For users a new version of their plugin\r\n\r\nIt doesn't seem like it would be the right call to remove the alpha API.\r\n\r\nThinking about this now though, we could probably look into having the alpha version call the v1 version and do the conversion in the alpha part of the code.\r\nIt might be a good followup PR :) !",
